#Skill:  Persuade wild men to remain [9586]
#
Usage:  USE @@@@ <savage>
Time:   seven days

Usage of @@@@ will induce a group of wild men to remain stacked with
the noble that summoned them.  An application of @@@@ will add two
months to the duration the wild men will stay with the noble, to a
maximum of four months.

The savage unit to be persuaded to remain must be specified as an
argument to USE @@@@.
